    <abstract>
      <t>   If QUIC is to be used in a peer-to-peer manner, with NAT traversal,
   then it is necessary to be able to demultiplex QUIC and other
   protocols used in WebRTC on a single UDP port. This memo discusses
   options for demultiplexing.

	 </t>
